reviewText: 24 discs worth of classic looney tunes. Some I was familiar with but a lot I hadn't seen before & all these classics packaged in a wonderful box set. I will enjoy these for years to come

awesome! if you like those old school cartoons, this is a must!!! the only but here is that it arrived damaged, not the discs, but the cases (those little plastic things that hold the disc in place came broken) and the package had a "bump" right in wile e. coyote's hand, real shame! had to take out most of the DVDs and keep'em else!
